import {
  EachVideo,
  ThumbnailImage,
  DetailsCard,
  Description,
  ProfileLogo,
  ChannelName,
  PublishedAt,
  Views,
  Title,
} from './styledComponents'

const VideoCard = props => {
  const {videoData} = props

  const {
    channelName,
    id,
    profileImageUrl,
    publishedAt,
    thumbnailUrl,
    title,
    viewCount,
  } = videoData

  return (
    <EachVideo>
      <>
        <ThumbnailImage src={thumbnailUrl} alt="" />
        <DetailsCard>
          <ProfileLogo src={thumbnailUrl} alt="" />
          <Description>
            <Title>{title}</Title>
          </Description>
        </DetailsCard>
      </>
    </EachVideo>
  )
}
export default VideoCard
